         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>This Praśnāṣṭaka of the Āraṇa was copied by Sūryyanārāyaṇa, who was born in the
               Kauṇḍanya family (kula°). May the good ones forgive the mistake made by [my] hand.
               Year of Khara, month of Māgha, day 27 – the manuscript of the Āraṇam was fully copied
               for Somāskandagurukkaḷ, benefiting all people.</p>
         </div>
